{{book title|Technology Planning|The Educator's Guide}}
A '''technology plan''' is an important document for every educational institution. It is so important that some states, such as Pennsylvania, have incorporated the technology plan into the state-required strategic plan. This book is based on the knowledge, experience, and learnings of a group of graduate students and their professor.
This goal of this book is to offer insight and methodology into the best practices that should be followed to for a valid technology plan that is created, supported, and accepted by all stakeholders. This book is a work in progress and does not yet offer a complete step-by-step guide to Technology Planning. This book does aim to offer a starting point for others to follow and build upon.
